### **.gitignore**

Below is the `.gitignore` file to ensure unnecessary files are excluded from the repository:

```plaintext
# Byte-compiled / optimized / DLL files
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class

# Logs and database files
*.log
*.sqlite3

# Environment variables
.env
*.env

# Python virtual environment
/venv/

# OS-specific files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Application files
data/audio/
data/transcripts/
*.mp3
*.txt

# IDE and editor files
.vscode/
.idea/

# Jupyter Notebook checkpoints
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# Miscellaneous
*.bak
*.swp
